{"lemma":"خَصاصَةٍ","slug":"خَصاصَةٍ","root":"خ.ص.ص","root_slug":"خ-ص-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ص-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"خَصاصَةٍ","root":"خصص","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10740","n10741"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D8%B5%D8%A7%D8%B5%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"crack, opening","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"interstice, interval","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"deficit, lack, shortage, shortfall; want, need, poverty, destitution","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"straitness, difficulty","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of خُصّ (ḵuṣṣ, “booth”)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10740","headword_ar":"خَصَاصَةٌ","root":"xS","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An interstice, interval,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intervening space"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"opening;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSaASN","text_ar":"خَصَاصٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is commonly used as a coll. gen. n.] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSaASaA='u","text_ar":"خَصَاصَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an interstice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vagor","text_ar":"ثَغْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"front teeth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as also ↓ the second of these words: (TA:) or the first and ↓ second, (TA,) or ↓ all, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any interstice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hole"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perforation, in a door, and sieve, and"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"veil of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buroquE","text_ar":"بُرْقُع"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as a cloud, and a strainer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (TA:) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a crevice, cranny, chink,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fissure:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or the first, (TA,) or ↓ all, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small hole"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perforation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or the first has this signification as well as the signification first mentioned: (S:) or the ↓ second, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaw~ap","text_ar":"كَوَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mural aperture"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"structure of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qub~ap","text_ar":"قُبَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"or the like, when as wide as the face;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to some,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether wide or narrow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and the same,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interstices, intervals,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intervening spaces"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"openings,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuS~","text_ar":"خُصّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narrow interstices,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., therein: (T, TA:) and the same, (TA,) or ↓ all, (K,) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intervening spaces between the three stones upon which a cooking-pot is placed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between the fingers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and the first, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intervening spaces between the feathers of an arrow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA:) pl. [of the first,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSaASaAtN","text_ar":"خَصَاصَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) You say of the moon,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"badaA mino xaSaASapi Algayomi","text_ar":"بَدَا مِنْ خَصَاصَةِ الغَيْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It appeared from the gap of the cloud,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clouds"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, A.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cloud"},{"kind":"text","text":"itself; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clouds;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayomN","text_ar":"غَيْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-  Also the first, (S, A, Mgh, Msb, K,) and ↓ second, (S, K,) and ↓ third, (IDrd, K,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Poverty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"need;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straitness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"difficulty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an evil state"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSaASaAt","text_ar":"خَصَاصَات"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning the “ holes ” of a sieve: whence a saying cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajam~ala","text_ar":"تَجَمَّلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) or from the first of the senses explained in this paragraph; because a thing, when it opens so as to form an interstice, becomes weak and unsound. (TA.) You say also, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sadadotu xuSaASapa","text_ar":"سَدَدْتُ خُصَاصَةَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnK","text_ar":"فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with damm, meaning, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I repaired the broken fortune of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also the first, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thirst;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in camels when they return from water without having satisfied themselves with drink: and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hunger;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in a man when he has not satisfied himself with food. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","S","T","IAar","A","Mgh","Msb","IDrd"]},{"entry_id":"n10741","headword_ar":"خُصَاصَةٌ","root":"xS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaSaASapN","text_ar":"خَصَاصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence but one."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}